.TH "tennis" "1" "2026-04-03"
.P
.SH NAME
.P
tennis - print stylish CSV tables in your terminal
.P
https://github.\&com/gurgeous/tennis
.P
.SH SYNOPSIS
.P
\fBtennis\fR [\fIoptions.\&.\&.\&\fR] <file.\&csv>
.P
Also supports stdin, json/jsonl files, etc.\&
.P
.SH DESCRIPTION
.P
\fBtennis\fR is a small CLI for printing stylish CSV tables in your terminal.\&
Rows will be truncated to fit and it'\&ll automatically pick nice colors
to match your terminal.\& Works with all \fBCSV\fR variants as well as
\fBJSON/JSONL\fR.\& Written in zig.\&
.P
.SH DEMO
.P
